{"type":"message","id":"f408c641","parentId":"fffb53f3","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:47:54.516Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\"更新qa服务器\" - 这是服务端更新，不是客户端热更。根据 TOOLS.md 的记录，\"更新qa服\" 默认走 1v1 项目的 DevOps 流水线，dest=1v1_qa。\n\n这需要用 DevOps 流水线，Playwright 操作。这是耗时任务，需要开子 session。\n\n先回复收到，然后确认是服务端还是客户端。但根据 MEMORY.md：\n\"说「更新qa服务器」或「更新qa服」默认走 1v1 项目，dest=1v1_qa\"\n\n\n所以这里说的是\"服务器\"，应该就是服务端更新。根据记录，这对应 .NET 的 DevOps 流水线，dest 设为 1v1_qa。我先发消息确认收到，然后开子 session 来执行这个耗时的流水线操作。\n\n不过我对 DevOps 流水线的具体实现还不太确定——TOOLS.md 提到用 Playwright 打开流水线页面并点击启动，但没有给出具体的脚本路径，可能需要先检查一下 workspace/scripts 目录里有没有相关的脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01XmppabT5pwADi6XWveGjpZ","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","message":"收到，开始更新1v1_qa服 🌸"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01VgwSMhmf4aRkmk93PRo555","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\ | Where-Object { $_.Name -like \"*devops*\" -or $_.Name -like \"*pipeline*\" }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779194860341,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1ad484dc-5954-4f20-8918-d028c187aadb"}}
