{"type":"message","id":"5a28ae50","parentId":"67175442","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:47:55.367Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01VgwSMhmf4aRkmk93PRo555","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ŀ¼: C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     18:55           3733 devops_keepalive.mjs                                                 \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     20:39           5220 devops_poll_build.mjs                                                \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     20:41           5572 devops_poll_v2.mjs                                                   \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     20:42           7113 devops_poll_v3.mjs                                                   \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     20:34           8247 devops_trigger_build.mjs                                             \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     20:37          11547 devops_trigger_build_v2.mjs                                          \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     20:38           7579 devops_trigger_build_v3.mjs"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":309,"aggregated":"Ŀ¼: C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     18:55           3733 devops_keepalive.mjs                                                 \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     20:39           5220 devops_poll_build.mjs                                                \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     20:41           5572 devops_poll_v2.mjs                                                   \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     20:42           7113 devops_poll_v3.mjs                                                   \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     20:34           8247 devops_trigger_build.mjs                                             \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     20:37          11547 devops_trigger_build_v2.mjs                                          \r\n-a----         2026/5/19     20:38           7579 devops_trigger_build_v3.mjs","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779194875367}}
{"type":"message","id":"d30d6dfe","parentId":"5a28ae50","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:47:58.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01AfzGw1YRCYLdPBKQmpqb1q","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_trigger_build_v3.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779194875368,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3f31c71f-704e-46f6-ba22-86acbcad6808"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fc19fd56","parentId":"d30d6dfe","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:47:59.026Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01AfzGw1YRCYLdPBKQmpqb1q","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// DevOps Build Trigger Script v3\n// Properly closes dropdown before clicking start button\n//\n// Usage: node devops_trigger_build_v3.mjs <pipelineId> <dest>\n\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'devops_cookies.json');\n\nconst PIPELINE_ID = process.argv[2] || 'p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a';\nconst DEST = process.argv[3] || '1v1_qa';\n\nfunction log(msg) {\n  console.log(`[${new Date().toISOString()}] ${msg}`);\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  log(`Loaded ${cookies.length} cookies`);\n\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless: true,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'],\n  });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({\n    locale: 'zh-CN',\n    viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 },\n    ignoreHTTPSErrors: true,\n  });\n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n\n  // Track API responses for build trigger confirmation\n  let triggeredBuildId = null;\n  page.on('response', async (resp) => {\n    const url = resp.url();\n    if (resp.request().method() === 'POST' && (url.includes('/builds') || url.includes('/build'))) {\n      try {\n        const body = await resp.text().catch(() => '');\n        log(`Build API [${resp.status()}] ${url.substring(0, 120)}: ${body.substring(0, 300)}`);\n        const match = body.match(/\"data\"\\s*:\\s*\"(b-[a-z0-9]+)\"/);\n        if (match) triggeredBuildId = match[1];\n      } catch {}\n    }\n  });\n\n  try {\n    const pipelineUrl = `https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/${PIPELINE_ID}`;\n    log(`Opening: ${pipelineUrl}`);\n    await page.goto(pipelineUrl, { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 40000 });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n    const pageUrl = page.url();\n    if (pageUrl.includes('login')) {\n      log('❌ Session expired');\n      process.exit(1);\n    }\n\n    // Click \"启动新构建\"\n    log('Clicking 启动新构建...');\n    await page.click('button:has-text(\"启动新构建\")');\n    await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n    // Verify dialog appeared\n    const selects = await page.locator('.ant-select').count();\n    log(`Dialog selects count: ${selects}`);\n    \n    if (selects === 0) {\n      log('Dialog may not have appeared');\n    }\n\n    // Get current value of first select (dest)\n    const destCurrentValue = await page.evaluate(() => {\n      const firstSelect = document.querySelector('.ant-select');\n      return firstSelect ? firstSelect.innerText.trim() : 'not found';\n    });\n    log(`Dest current value: ${destCurrentValue}`);\n\n    if (destCurrentValue === DEST) {\n      log(`✅ dest already set to ${DEST}, no change needed`);\n    } else {\n      // Need to change the dest value\n      log(`Changing dest from \"${destCurrentValue}\" to \"${DEST}\"...`);\n      \n      // Click the first select to open dropdown\n      const firstSelect = page.locator('.ant-select').first();\n      await firstSelect.click();\n      await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n      \n      // Wait for dropdown to appear\n      await page.waitForSelector('.ant-select-dropdown', { timeout: 5000 }).catch(() => {\n        log('Dropdown not appeared via .ant-select-dropdown');\n      });\n      \n      // Find and click the option\n      const optionLocator = page.locator(`.ant-select-item:has-text(\"${DEST}\"), .ant-select-dropdown li:has-text(\"${DEST}\")`).first();\n      const optionCount = await optionLocator.count();\n      log(`Options for ${DEST}: ${optionCount}`);\n      \n      if (optionCount > 0) {\n        await optionLocator.click();\n        log(`✅ Selected ${DEST}`);\n      } else {\n        // List all options\n        const allOptions = await page.evaluate(() => {\n          const opts = document.querySelectorAll('.ant-select-item, .ant-select-item-option');\n          return Array.from(opts).map(o => o.innerText || o.title).filter(Boolean);\n        });\n        log(`Available options: ${JSON.stringify(allOptions)}`);\n        \n        if (allOptions.length > 0) {\n          // Try to find close match\n          const match = allOptions.find(o => o.includes(DEST) || DEST.includes(o));\n          if (match) {\n            await page.click(`.ant-select-item:has-text(\"${match}\")`);\n            log(`✅ Selected closest match: ${match}`);\n          } else {\n            log(`⚠️ Could not find ${DEST} in options`);\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n\n    // Press Escape to close any open dropdown, then wait\n    await page.keyboard.press('Escape');\n    await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n\n    // Take screenshot to verify state\n    await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', 'devops_v3_before_start.png') });\n    log('Screenshot: devops_v3_before_start.png');\n\n    // Now click the \"启动\" button using JavaScript to avoid overlay issues\n    log('Clicking 启动 button via JavaScript...');\n    const clicked = await page.evaluate(() => {\n      // Find the primary button in the modal footer\n      const modalFooter = document.querySelector('.ant-modal-footer, .ant-modal-content');\n      if (!modalFooter) return { success: false, reason: 'no modal footer' };\n      \n      const buttons = Array.from(modalFooter.querySelectorAll('button'));\n      const startBtn = buttons.find(b => b.innerText.includes('启动') && !b.innerText.includes('新构建'));\n      \n      if (startBtn) {\n        startBtn.click();\n        return { success: true, text: startBtn.innerText };\n      }\n      \n      // Try any primary button\n      const primaryBtn = buttons.find(b => b.className.includes('primary'));\n      if (primaryBtn) {\n        primaryBtn.click();\n        return { success: true, text: primaryBtn.innerText, type: 'primary' };\n      }\n      \n      return { success: false, reason: `buttons found: ${buttons.map(b => b.innerText).join(', ')}` };\n    });\n    log(`JS click result: ${JSON.stringify(clicked)}`);\n\n    await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n    await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', 'devops_v3_after_start.png') });\n    \n    // Check result\n    const finalUrl = page.url();\n    const finalText = await page.evaluate(() => document.body.innerText.substring(0, 1500));\n    log(`Final URL: ${finalUrl}`);\n    log(`Final text: ${finalText.substring(0, 400)}`);\n\n    // Check for success indicators\n    const buildIdInUrl = finalUrl.match(/buildId=(b-[a-z0-9]+)/);\n    const buildNumInText = finalText.match(/#(\\d+)/g);\n    \n    if (buildIdInUrl) triggeredBuildId = buildIdInUrl[1];\n    \n    // Save refreshed cookies\n    const newCookies = await ctx.cookies();\n    fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(newCookies, null, 2));\n    log(`Saved ${newCookies.length} cookies`);\n\n    if (triggeredBuildId || (clicked.success && buildNumInText)) {\n      log(`✅ SUCCESS! Build triggered. ID: ${triggeredBuildId || 'unknown'}, Build: ${buildNumInText ? buildNumInText[0] : 'unknown'}`);\n      await browser.close();\n      process.exit(0);\n    } else {\n      log(`⚠️ Uncertain result. clicked=${JSON.stringify(clicked)}`);\n      await browser.close();\n      process.exit(1);\n    }\n\n  } catch (e) {\n    log(`ERROR: ${e.message}`);\n    try {\n      await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', 'devops_v3_error.png') });\n    } catch {}\n    try { await browser.close(); } catch {}\n    process.exit(2);\n  }\n}\n\nmain();\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779194879026}}
{"type":"message","id":"81254512","parentId":"fc19fd56","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:48:02.022Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01GzcYhYbsB2WX5FB9mmeecU","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_poll_v3.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779194879027,"responseId":"chatcmpl-88a1dc58-a9d9-4a76-abbd-aadf919c70ea"}}
{"type":"message","id":"67c8e92f","parentId":"81254512","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:48:02.205Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01GzcYhYbsB2WX5FB9mmeecU","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// DevOps Build Status Poller v3\n// Captures build status from network API calls on the main pipeline page\n//\n// Usage: node devops_poll_v3.mjs <pipelineId> <buildId>\n\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'devops_cookies.json');\n\nconst PIPELINE_ID = process.argv[2] || 'p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a';\nconst BUILD_ID = process.argv[3] || '';\nconst MAX_WAIT_MINUTES = parseInt(process.argv[4] || '25');\n\nfunction log(msg) {\n  console.log(`[${new Date().toISOString()}] ${msg}`);\n}\n\nconst SUCCESS_STATUSES = ['succeed', 'success'];\nconst FAIL_STATUSES = ['failed', 'failure', 'canceled', 'terminate', 'heartbeat_timeout'];\n\nasync function checkBuildOnce(cookies) {\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless: true,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox'],\n  });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({\n    locale: 'zh-CN',\n    viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 },\n    ignoreHTTPSErrors: true,\n  });\n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n\n  let buildStatus = null;\n  let buildResult = null;\n  const capturedApis = [];\n\n  page.on('response', async (resp) => {\n    const url = resp.url();\n    // Capture ALL API responses to learn the API structure\n    if (url.includes('/ms/') || url.includes('/api/')) {\n      try {\n        const body = await resp.text().catch(() => '');\n        if (body.length > 5 && body.length < 20000 && body.includes('{')) {\n          capturedApis.push({ url: url.substring(0, 150), status: resp.status(), body: body.substring(0, 500) });\n          \n          // Try to parse and find build status\n          try {\n            const data = JSON.parse(body);\n            const checkObj = (obj, depth = 0) => {\n              if (!obj || typeof obj !== 'object' || depth > 5) return;\n              \n              // Check for build ID reference\n              const str = JSON.stringify(obj).toLowerCase();\n              if (str.includes(BUILD_ID.toLowerCase()) || str.includes('b-f5c3bf')) {\n                log(`Found build reference in: ${url.substring(0, 80)}`);\n                log(`  Data: ${JSON.stringify(obj).substring(0, 300)}`);\n                \n                const s = obj.status || obj.buildStatus || obj.buildStatusDesc;\n                const r = obj.result || obj.buildResult;\n                if (s && !buildStatus) buildStatus = String(s);\n                if (r && !buildResult) buildResult = String(r);\n              }\n            };\n            \n            checkObj(data);\n            if (data.data) checkObj(data.data);\n            if (Array.isArray(data.data)) data.data.forEach(item => checkObj(item));\n          } catch {}\n        }\n      } catch {}\n    }\n  });\n\n  try {\n    // Use the URL with buildId query param that worked before\n    const buildUrl = `https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/${PIPELINE_ID}?buildId=${BUILD_ID}`;\n    log(`Navigating to: ${buildUrl}`);\n    await page.goto(buildUrl, { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 40000 });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n    const currentUrl = page.url();\n    const pageText = await page.evaluate(() => document.body.innerText.substring(0, 3000));\n    log(`URL: ${currentUrl}`);\n    log(`Page (first 500): ${pageText.substring(0, 500)}`);\n    \n    // Log all captured APIs\n    log(`\\nCaptured ${capturedApis.length} API calls:`);\n    capturedApis.slice(0, 15).forEach(a => {\n      log(`  [${a.status}] ${a.url}`);\n    });\n    \n    // Try to find status from page content\n    if (!buildStatus) {\n      // Look for status indicators in the page\n      const statusMap = {\n        '运行中': 'RUNNING',\n        'Running': 'RUNNING', \n        '排队中': 'QUEUE',\n        '成功': 'SUCCEED',\n        '失败': 'FAILED',\n        '已取消': 'CANCELED',\n      };\n      \n      for (const [text, status] of Object.entries(statusMap)) {\n        if (pageText.includes(text)) {\n          buildStatus = status;\n          log(`Found status from page text: ${text} → ${status}`);\n          break;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n\n    // Check for specific build detail on page\n    // The page shows build history - look for #1086 status\n    const buildNumMatch = pageText.match(/#1086[\\s\\S]{0,200}/);\n    if (buildNumMatch) {\n      log(`Build #1086 context: ${buildNumMatch[0].substring(0, 200)}`);\n    }\n    \n    // Try to find the actual build status from network responses by trying the API directly\n    const devopsToken = cookies.find(c => c.name === 'devops_token')?.value;\n    if (devopsToken) {\n      log('\\nTrying direct API with token...');\n      const resp = await fetch(`https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/ms/process/api/user/builds/yyzy/${PIPELINE_ID}/${BUILD_ID}`, {\n        headers: {\n          'Cookie': `devops_token=${devopsToken}`,\n          'Accept': 'application/json',\n          'X-DEVOPS-PROJECT-ID': 'yyzy',\n        }\n      });\n      const body = await resp.text();\n      log(`Direct API [${resp.status}]: ${body.substring(0, 500)}`);\n      \n      if (resp.status === 200) {\n        try {\n          const data = JSON.parse(body);\n          const s = data?.data?.status || data?.data?.buildStatus;\n          if (s) buildStatus = s;\n          log(`API status: ${s}`);\n        } catch {}\n      }\n    }\n\n  } catch (e) {\n    log(`Error: ${e.message}`);\n  } finally {\n    const newCookies = await ctx.cookies();\n    fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(newCookies, null, 2));\n    await browser.close();\n  }\n  \n  return { status: buildStatus, result: buildResult };\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  log(`Polling build ${BUILD_ID}`);\n\n  const startTime = Date.now();\n  const maxMs = MAX_WAIT_MINUTES * 60 * 1000;\n  let attempt = 0;\n\n  while (Date.now() - startTime < maxMs) {\n    attempt++;\n    log(`\\n=== Poll #${attempt} ===`);\n    \n    const freshCookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n    const { status, result } = await checkBuildOnce(freshCookies);\n    \n    log(`\\nResult: status=${status || 'unknown'}, result=${result || 'unknown'}`);\n    \n    const checkStr = `${status || ''} ${result || ''}`.toLowerCase();\n    \n    if (SUCCESS_STATUSES.some(s => checkStr.includes(s))) {\n      log('✅ BUILD SUCCEEDED!');\n      console.log('FINAL_STATUS:SUCCESS');\n      process.exit(0);\n    }\n    \n    if (FAIL_STATUSES.some(s => checkStr.includes(s))) {\n      log('❌ BUILD FAILED!');\n      console.log('FINAL_STATUS:FAILED');\n      process.exit(1);\n    }\n    \n    if (attempt === 1) {\n      // On first poll, just learn the API structure; don't wait too long\n      log('First poll complete. Waiting 60s before next check...');\n      await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 60000));\n    } else {\n      log('Waiting 60s...');\n      await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 60000));\n    }\n  }\n\n  log('TIMEOUT');\n  console.log('FINAL_STATUS:TIMEOUT');\n  process.exit(2);\n}\n\nmain();\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779194882205}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9bd5b44","parentId":"67c8e92f","timestamp":"2026-05-19T12:48:20.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，有现成的脚本。开子 session 来触发 DevOps 1v1_qa 流水线并轮询结果。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01LvwEtHaWT7U2cYgmmyQ94R","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"触发 DevOps 1v1-测试服流水线（dest=1v1_qa），并等待构建完成，然后通过飞书消息通知指派人。\n\n**步骤：**\n\n1. 触发构建：\n```\nnode C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_trigger_build_v3.mjs p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a 1v1_qa\n```\n- 退出码 0 → 触发成功，继续轮询\n- 退出码 1 → Cookie 失效（登录过期），报告失败\n- 退出码 2 → 脚本错误，报告失败\n\n2. 从脚本日志中提取 Build ID（格式 `b-xxxxxxxx`），例如 `✅ SUCCESS! Build triggered. ID: b-f5c3bf...`\n\n3. 轮询构建状态（最多等 25 分钟）：\n```\nnode C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_poll_v3.mjs p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a <buildId>\n```\n- 输出包含 `FINAL_STATUS:SUCCESS` → 成功\n- 输出包含 `FINAL_STATUS:FAILED` → 失败\n- 输出包含 `FINAL_STATUS:TIMEOUT` → 超时（当作失败处理）\n\n4. 构建完成后，用 message tool 发送飞书私信给主人（Yousan 叶枝君，open_id: `ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f`）：\n   - 成功：「1v1_qa服更新完成 ✅」\n   - 失败：「1v1_qa服更新失败 ❌，请检查 DevOps 日志」\n\n**注意：**\n- Cookie 文件：`C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\devops_cookies.json`\n- 发飞书私信用 message tool（action=send, channel=feishu, target=user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f）\n- 不要发群消息，直接私信主人即可","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":2400}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779194882206,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7733f3c8-d31b-4c7f-8296-b8be2679339c"}}
